e Archer 3]]'' (1981)<br />** * ''[[The Brave Archer and His Mate]]'' (1982)<br />''[[The Eagle Shooting Heroes|Se diu ying hung ji dung sing sai jau]]'' (''The Eagle Shooting Heroes'') (1993)<br />''[[Ashes of Time|Dongxi\u00e9 Xid\u00fa]]'' (''Ashes of Time'') (1994)\n|-\n| ''She Loves Me Not'' (1933), Edward Hope\n| ''[[She Loves Me Not (1934 film)|She Loves Me Not]]'' (1934)<br />''[[True to the Army]]'' (1942)<br />''[[How to Be Very, Very Popular]]'' (1955)\n|-\n| ''[[Sheep (novel)|Sheep]]'' (2004), [[Simon Maginn]]\n| ''[[The Dark (film)|The Dark]]'' (2005)\n|-\n| ''Shen Mu'' (''Sacred Wood'') (1999), Liu Qingbang\n| ''[[Blind Shaft]]'' (2003)\n|-\n| ''A Shilling for Candles'' (1936), [[Josephine Tey]] (pseudonym for Elizabeth MacKintosh)\n| ''[[Young and Innocent]]'' (1937)\n|-\n| ''[[The Shining (novel)|The Shining]]'' (1977), [[Stephen King]]\n| ''[[The Shining (film)|The Shining]]'' (1980)<br />''[[The Shining (TV miniseries)|The Shining]]'' (1997) (TV)\n|-\n| ''Shining Through'' (1988), [[Susan Isaacs]]\n| ''[[Shining Through]]'' (1992)\n|-\n| ''[[The Shipping News]]'' (1993), [[Annie Proulx]]\n| ''[[The Shipping News (film)|The Shipping News]]'' (2001)\n|-\n| ''[[The Shrinking Man]]'' (1956), [[Richard Matheson]]\n| ''[[The Incredible Shrinking Man]]'' (1957)<br />''[[The Incredible Shrinking Woman]]'' (1981)\n|-\n| ''[[The Shoes of the Fisherman (novel)|The Shoes of the Fisherman]]'' (1963), [[Morris West]]\n| ''[[The Shoes of the Fisherman]]'' (1968)\n|-\n| ''[[Shoeless Joe (novel)|Shoeless Joe]]'' (1982), [[W. P. Kinsella]]\n| ''[[Field of Dreams]]'' (1989)\n|-\n| ''The Shootist'' (1975), [[Glendon Swarthout]]\n| ''[[The Shootist]]'' (1976)\n|-\n| ''Shout at the Devil'' (1968), [[Wilbur Smith]]\n| ''[[Shout at the Devil (film)|Shout at the Devil]]'' (1976)\n|-\n| ''[[Shutter Island]]'' (2003), [[Dennis Lehane]]\n| ''[[Shutter Island (film)|Shutter Island]]'' (2010)\n|-\n| ''[[Sideways (novel)|Sideways]]'' (2004), [[Rex Pickett]]\n| ''[[Sideways]]'' (