 Down]]'' (1935), [[A. J. Cronin]]\n| ''[[The Stars Look Down (film)|The Stars Look Down]]'' (1939)\n|-\n| ''[[Starship Troopers]]'' (1959), [[Robert A. Heinlein]]\n| ''[[Starship Troopers (film)|Starship Troopers]]'' (1997)<br />* ''[[Starship Troopers 2: Hero of the Federation]]'' (2004)<br />** ''[[Starship Troopers 3: Marauder]]'' (2007)\n|-\n| ''Station West'' (1948), [[Luke Short (writer)|Luke Short]]\n| ''[[Station West]]'' (1948)\n|-\n| ''[[The Stepford Wives]]'' (1972), [[Ira Levin]]\n| ''[[The Stepford Wives (1975 film)|The Stepford Wives]]'' (1975)<br />* ''[[Revenge of the Stepford Wives]]'' (1980) (TV)<br />** ''[[The Stepford Children]]'' (1987) (TV)<br />** * ''[[The Stepford Husbands]]'' (1996) (TV)<br />''[[The Stepford Wives (2004 film)|The Stepford Wives]]'' (2004)\n|-\n| ''[[Stella Dallas (novel)|Stella Dallas]]'' (1923), [[Olive Higgins Prouty]]\n| ''[[Stella Dallas (1925 film)|Stella Dallas]]'' (1925)<br />''[[Stella Dallas (1937 film)|Stella Dallas]]'' (1937)<br />''[[Stella (1990 film)|Stella]]'' (1990)\n|-\n| ''[[A Stir of Echoes]]'' (1958), [[Richard Matheson]]\n| ''[[Stir of Echoes]]'' (1999)<br />* ''[[Stir of Echoes: The Homecoming]]'' (2007)\n|-\n| ''Storm in the City'' (1950), [[Horace McCoy]]\n| ''[[The Turning Point (1952 film)|The Turning Point]]'' (1952)\n|-\n| ''[[Strange Case of Dr Jekyll and Mr Hyde]]'' (1886), [[Robert Louis Stevenson]]\n| ''[[Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde (1908 film)|Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde]]'' (1908)<br />''[[Adaptations of Strange Case of Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde#Den Sk\u00e6bnesvangre Opfindelse|Den Sk\u00e6bnesvangre Opfindelse]]'' (''Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde'') (1910)<br />''[[Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde (1912 film)|Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde]]'' (1912)<br />''[[Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde (1913 film)|Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde]]'' (1913)<br />''[[Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde (1920 film)|Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde]]'' (1920)<br />''[[Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde (1920/II film)|Dr. Jekyll and Mr. Hyde]]'' (1920)<br />''[[The Head of Janus|D