ien ik]]'' (''Business Is Business'') (1971)\n|-\n| ''[[A Watcher in the Woods]]'' (1976), Florence Engel Randall\n| ''[[The Watcher in the Woods (1980 film)|The Watcher in the Woods]]'' (1980)\n|-\n| ''[[Water for Elephants]]'' (2006), [[Sara Gruen]]\n| ''[[Water for Elephants (film)|Water for Elephants]]'' (2011)\n|-\n| ''The Water Hole'' (1927\u20131928) (serial) (1928) (novel), [[Zane Grey]]\n| ''[[The Water Hole]]'' (1928)\n|-\n| ''[[Watership Down]]'' (1972), [[Richard Adams]]\n| ''[[Watership Down (film)|Watership Down]]'' (1978)\n|-\n| ''[[The Way West]]'' (1949), [[A. B. Guthrie, Jr.]]\n| ''[[The Way West (film)|The Way West]]'' (1967)\n|-\n| ''[[The Werewolf of Paris]]'' (1933), [[Guy Endore]]\n| ''[[The Curse of the Werewolf]]'' (1961)<br />''[[Legend of the Werewolf]]'' (1975)\n|-\n| ''West of the Pecos'' (1937), [[Zane Grey]]\n| ''[[Zane Grey#Films based on his novels - West of the Pecos (1922)|West of the Pecos]]'' (1922)<br />''[[Zane Grey#Films based on his novels - West of the Pecos (1934)|West of the Pecos]]'' (1934)<br />''[[Zane Grey#Films based on his novels - West of the Pecos (1945)|West of the Pecos]]'' (1945)\n|-\n| ''[[The Wet Parade]]'' (1931), [[Upton Sinclair]]\n| ''The Wet Parade'' (1932)\n|-\n| ''[[We're Back! A Dinosaur's Story (book)|We're Back! A Dinosaur's Story]]'' (1987), [[Hudson Talbott]]\n| ''[[We're Back! A Dinosaur's Story (film)|We're Back! A Dinosaur's Story]]'' (1993)\n|-\n| ''[[What Dreams May Come]]'' (1978), [[Richard Matheson]]\n| ''[[What Dreams May Come (film)|What Dreams May Come]]'' (1998)\n|-\n| ''What's the Worst Thing That Could Happen?'' (1996), [[Donald E. Westlake]]\n| ''[[What's the Worst Thing That Could Happen?]]'' (2001)\n|-\n| ''The Wheels Spins'' (1936), [[Ethel Lina White]]\n| ''[[The Lady Vanishes (1938 film)|The Lady Vanishes]]'' (1938)<br />''[[The Lady Vanishes (1979 film)|The Lady Vanishes]]'' (1979)\n|-\n| ''[[When Eight Bells Toll]]'' (1966), [[Alistair MacLean]]\n| ''[[When Eight Bells Toll (1