 his novels - Wild Horse Mesa (1925)|Wild Horse Mesa]]'' (1925)<br />''[[Zane Grey#Film based on his novels - Wild Horse Mesa (1932)|Wild Horse Mesa]]'' (1932)<br />''[[Zane Grey#Film based on his novels - Wild Horse Mesa (1947)|Wild Horse Mesa]]'' (1947)\n|-\n| ''Wild Justice'' (1979), [[Wilbur Smith]]\n| ''Wild Justice'' (a. k. a. ''Covert Assassin'') (1993) (TV)\n|-\n| ''[[The Willing Flesh]]'' (1955), [[Willi Heinrich]]\n| ''[[Cross of Iron]]'' (1977)\n|-\n| ''[[Wilt (novel)|Wilt]]'' (1976), [[Tom Sharpe]]\n| ''[[Wilt (film)|Wilt]]'' (1989)\n|-\n| ''[[The Wind in the Willows]]'' (1908), [[Kenneth Grahame]]\n| ''[[The Adventures of Ichabod and Mr. Toad]]'' (1949)<br />''[[The Wind in the Willows (1983 film)|The Wind in the Willows]]'' (1983)<br />* ''[[The Wind in the Willows (TV series)#A Tale of Two Toads|The Wind in the Willows: A Tale of Two Toads]]'' (1989) (TV)<br />''[[The Wind in the Willows (1987 film)|The Wind in the Willows]]'' (1987) (TV)<br />''[[The Wind in the Willows#1995 film|The Wind in the Willows]]'' (1995) (TV)<br />* ''[[The Wind in the Willows#The Willows in Winter (1996 film)|The Willows in Winter]]'' (1996)<br />''[[The Wind in the Willows (1996 film)|The Wind in the Willows]]'' (1996)<br />''[[The Wind in the Willows (2006 film)|The Wind in the Willows]]'' (2006) (TV)<br />''[[The Wind in the Willows#In 2010, it was announced that Ray Griggs was developing a live-action/CGI blend adaptation of the story, scheduled to begin filming in late 2010 in New Zealand.|The Wind in the Willows]]'' (2012)\n|-\n| ''[[The Wings of the Dove]]'' (1902), [[Henry James]]\n| ''[[The Wings of the Dove (1981 film)|The Wings of the Dove]]'' (1981)<br />''[[The Wings of the Dove (1997 film)|The Wings of the Dove]]'' (1997)\n|-\n| ''[[Winnie-the-Pooh]]'' (1926\u20131928) (series), [[A.A. Milne]]<br />''[[Winnie-the-Pooh (book)|Winnie-the-Pooh]]'' (1926)<br />* ''[[The House at Pooh Corner]]'' (1928)\n| ''[[Winnie the Pooh (franchise)|Disney's Winnie the Pooh]]'